RIFTSMUD: About the Game

RiftsMUD is a text-based roleplaying game set in Palladium Books' Rifts
universe. The Third World War crippled Earth. The dead fed the ley lines,
rifts tore open, and monsters, magic, and other worlds poured through.

This recreation is built on the Nightmare III mudlib running FluffOS 2.9.
The original RiftsMUD 2.1 was one of the longest-running Rifts MUDs on
the web, with over 50 races, 50 Occupational Character Classes, 150 skills,
and locations such as Chi-Town, New Camelot, Splynn, Lazlo, and NGR.

Player memories of the original include: minimal color (green exits, green
radio, red/white OOC, blue tells), Moxim the rift opener, ley line travel,
psi-swords and flame hilts, pet hawks from falconry, and deep zone content
from Praxis to Atlantis and Europe.

